OOC: I'm waiting for everyone to post for the patrol but since they 
don't seem to respond....

BIC:

Warhead's sensors detected something that seemed very important. He 
stopped, skidded a few meters because of his hovering and called his 
patrol.

Warhead: Everyone, gather to my position. I detect a tremendous 
energon mass in the ground. The radiation levels are nearly off the 
scales! That's simply amazing! Let's take extra readouts before we 
report back to base. Inferno and Rage, you'll scan the mass of this 
energon cluster. Nightshade, determine its stability. Drillbit, find 
out at what depth it is. I'll try to take a sample after I know all 
this.

He waits for his team to report back

OOC: For your knowledge, it is a sphere of energon, of variable 
stability and buried at about 20 meters in the ground.
